our own gui that connect through an api. For each customer we will have at
least 2 VLAN's, this will mean a lot of vlan's.
Suppose we have 30 hosts, and 60 vlans.
- Now we add host 31, we will have to add all 60 VLANS to host 31. That is
a lot of clicking in the gui.
- we get a new customer, and add 2 vlans: on all 31 hosts we need to add
those 2 vlans, again a lot of work.

with my proposal:
add host 31:
map physical interfaces to host profile interfaces and you are done.
add customer:
add 2 vlans to a NIC in host profile and you are done."


